.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, photography, puzzles, sudoku, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: october, april, july, february, december, june
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person who's birthday is in june##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
12. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
13. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
14. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
15. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Hobby   | photography | woodworking | magic-tricks | sudoku | puzzles | cooking |
| Birthday     | july  | october  | april         | june | december    | february   |

