.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: american, argentine, british, canadian, polish, spanish
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, alhambra, siglo, blend, montecristo
 1. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 2. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
 3. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the alhambra-smoker is not to the left of the argentine##8
 5. the british is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 8. the canadian is not to the right of the canadian##8
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the british##5
10. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
11. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere between the polish and the alhambra-smoker##7
12. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
13. the spanish is between the blend-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2
14. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
15. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere between the montecristo-smoker and the american##7
16. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
17. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
18. the polish is the game-smoker##1
19. the alhambra-smoker is not the american##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | polish   | british | spanish    | canadian      | argentine | american |
| Cigar         | game | blend  | tiparillo | montecristo | alhambra   | siglo  |

