.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
There 6 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, pomegranate, radish, tomato, zucchini
6 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, bridge, mah-jongg, backgammon, domino
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 2. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 3. the person eating zucchini is between the person playing canasta and the person eating eggplant##2
 4. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person playing monopoly##7
 6. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 7. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 8. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 9. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
10. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
11. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
12. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person eating zucchini##7
13. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
14. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
16. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
17. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food    | eggplant | zucchini    | tomato     | radish  | pineapple    | pomegranate |
| Game   | monopoly  | backgammon | canasta | domino | bridge | mah-jongg     |

