.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-18::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, lemonade, milk, sprite
6 different pets are kept: snake, hamster, hedgehog, fish, cat, turtle
 1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
