 3. the owner of the cat is not the person drinking milk##6
 4. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 5. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
10. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
11. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
