 1. the software-developer is on the left of the chef##1
 2. the software-developer is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
 3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
 4. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
 5. the fan of rock is not to the left of the software-developer##8
 6. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 7. the freelancer is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 8. the fan of salsa is not the social-worker##6
 9. the scientist is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
10. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan of salsa##5
11. the freelancer is not the fan of rock##6
12. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
14. the fan of rock is in an odd position##4
15. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
16. the fan of techno is the freelancer##1
17. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
18. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
19. the scientist is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
20. the engineer is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5
